      "possibleIdentity": "Oliver Gordon Selfridge (1926–2008) was a pioneering mathematician and computer scientist who is often identified as the \"Father of Machine Perception.\" Although primarily a scientist, he was deeply involved in the intellectual and creative circles that intersected with art and technology during the late 1960s and early 1970s.
